{"tid":1737941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗拒捐無國界醫生組織外  仲有一樣野你可以做！！！","createTime":"2019-11-19T05:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T06:06:18.000Z","uid":144533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"494dd889afe18629d95d05b4d2877a2fd1dd1d94","tid":1737941,"uid":144533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"香港人抗爭六個月  就嚟半年啦！！<br />\n佢匿埋就半年依家出份聲明就同香港人割𥱊<br />\n火滾<br />\n你唔係俾呢個僞善者嘅醜聞沉底啊嘛<br />\n抗爭咁耐以來都有醫護人員因不同壓逼而抗議同罷工<br />\n咁值得社會迴響嘅事你唔係又俾佢慢慢沉底啊嘛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我依家有請所有香港人將呢次嘅新聞甚至你以後大部分嘅po同留言都加上hashtag </span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#SOSHK</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再用自己嘅方式share出去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不論你Google search爆佢又好<br />\n定用FB IG Twitter Reddit 咩都好<br />\n嚟多次好似NBA事件咁嘅熱潮<br />\n將#SOSHK再次推動全球關注<br />\n<br />\n我知好多人已經做緊#SOSHK，所以我哋更加要運用香港人多力量大呢個資源<br />\n香港人發出嘅聲音世界聽到啦<br />\n香港人都渴求嚟自世界嘅聲音"},{"pid":"be929e247a6a7f6499cf2789a85450fac6147591","tid":1737941,"uid":144533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:51:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#SOSHK</span>"},{"pid":"26df11519412e4129f2359e431715174181e48f7","tid":1737941,"uid":144533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#SOSHK</span>"},{"pid":"26c89da709d18039af1469e4f5a00aed115d92a7","tid":1737941,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:52:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n【行動】Twitter 戰線：世界各地政要火力全開！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入----------&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.m